description: Try our easy to follow Lolly Gobble Bliss Bombs Caramel Cupcakes recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Lolly Gobble Bliss Bombs Caramel Cupcakes
name: Lolly Gobble Bliss Bombs Caramel Cupcakes Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 Greens Anna Salted Caramel Cupcake Mix

recipeInstructions.text: Place frosting mix and soft butter into a small mixing bowl. Using an electric mixer, mix on low speed until combined. Mix on medium speed for a further 2 minutes. Spread prepared frosting on cooled cupcakes and top with Lolly Gobble Bliss Bombs.
